0Amrit%20Snan%20on%20Mauni%20Amavasya%20is%20the%20most%20significant%20ritual%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20occasion%20holds%20added%20spiritual%20importance%20due%20to%20a%20rare%20celestial%20alignment%20known%20as%20'Triveni%20Yog%2C'%20which%20occurs%20once%20every%20144%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh%202025%20has%20already%20witnessed%20over%2015%20crore%20pilgrims%20taking%20a%20holy%20dip%20in%20the%20past%2017%20days.%20Over%204.80%20crore%20devotees%20took%20the%20snan%20on%20Tuesday%20alone%20-%20even%20more%20than%20that%20of%20Amrit%20Snan'%20on%20Makar%20Sankranti%20(3.5%20crore)%2C%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maha%20Kumbh%20started%20on%20January%2013%20and%20will%20continue%20till%20February%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738133280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fhq80hj88_kumbh-modi_625x300_29_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flocal-administration-helping-victims-pm-modi-on-maha-kumbh-stampede-7584924%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20extended%20condolences%20even%20as%20casualties%20were%20feared%20after%20a%20stampede%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20fair%20grounds%20earlier%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20cam%3A%20US%20fighter%20jet%20crashes%20at%20Alaska%20base%2C%20pilot%20safe%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738133173000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117673199%2Cimgsize-3919222.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fon-cam-us-fighter-jet-crashes-at-alaska-base-pilot-safe%2Farticleshow%2F117672275.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20F-35%20fighter%20jet%20crashed%20at%20Eielson%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Alaska%2C%20with%20the%20pilot%20safely%20ejecting%20and%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20hospital%20for%20evaluation.%20The%20incident%20is%20under%20investigation.%20The%20base%20had%20recently%20undergone%20significant%20expansion%20to%20host%20these%20advanced%20aircraft%2C%20which%20have%20faced%20multiple%20recent%20incidents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fon-cam-us-fighter-jet-crashes-at-alaska-base-pilot-safe%2Farticleshow%2F117672275.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BUnconstitutional%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Junks%20Domicile-Based%20Medical%20Quotas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsupreme-court%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20struck%20down%20domicile-based%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20postgraduate%20medical%20courses%20-%20within%20the%20State%20quota%20-%20ruling%20it%20violative%20of%20Article%2014%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20is%20critical%20since%20it%20ensures%20that%20admission%20to%20PG%20medical%20courses%20-%20under%20quotas%20allotted%20to%20various%20states%20-%20can%20only%20be%20on%20merit%2C%20i.e.%2C%20on%20NEET%2C%20or%20National%20Eligibility%20%2F%20Entrance%20Test%2C%20scores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Hrishikesh%20Roy%2C%20Justice%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%2C%20and%20Justice%20SVN%20Bhatti%20said%20that%20as%20citizens%20and%20residents%20of%20India%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20residence%20anywhere...%20the%20Constitution%20also%20gives%20us%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20admission%20in%20educational%20institutions%20across%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20all%20domiciles%20in%20the%20territory%20of%20India.%20There%20is%20nothing%20like%20a%20provincial%20or%20state%20domicile...%20there%20is%20only%20one%20domicile.%20We%20are%20all%20residents%20of%20India.%20We%20have%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20residence%20anywhere%20in%20India%20and%20to%20carry%20out%20trade%20and%20profession%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConstitution%20also%20gives%20us%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20admission%20in%20educational%20institutions%20across%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20acknowledged%20reservations%20may%20be%20contemplated%20%26quot%3Bfor%20those%20who%20reside%20in%20a%20particular%20state%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20only%20in%20undergraduate%20courses.%20%26quot%3B...%20considering%20the%20importance%20of%20specialised%20doctors%2C%20reservation%20in%20higher%20levels%20-%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20residence%20-%20would%20be%20violative%20of%20Article%2014.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20an%20important%20aside%2C%20the%20court%20also%20said%20today's%20judgment%20would%20not%20affect%20domicile-based%20reservations%20already%20granted%2C%20and%20that%20students%20who%20had%20completed%20their%20degrees%20based%20on%20such%20selection%20criteria%20would%20not%20be%20affected%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20case%20dates%20back%20to%202019%2C%20when%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20heard%20appeals%20from%20a%20ruling%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20ruled%20similarly%2C%20i.e.%2C%20domicile-based%20reservations%20for%20PG%20medical%20courses%20are%20unconstitutional.%20However%2C%20the%20court%2C%20recongising%20the%20importance%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20two-judge%20bench%20referred%20the%20matter%20to%20a%20three-judge%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738132980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fah2nk1so_supreme-court_625x300_26_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-news-domicile-based-reservation-pg-