ion%20drama%2C%20with%20Antony%20scoring%20the%20music.%20'Parashakthi'%20is%20slated%20for%20a%20summer%20release%20and%20will%20compete%20with%20other%20big%20films.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fvijay-antonys-25th-films-title-and-first-look-revealed-makers-aim-for-summer-2025-release%2Farticleshow%2F117672436.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20A%20Record%20Number%20Of%20US%20Firms%20Are%20Leaving%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20newly%20elected%20U.S.%20President%2C%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20is%20making%20a%20pitch%20to%20reshore%20manufacturing%20to%20America%2C%20its%20companies%20operating%20out%20of%20China%20are%20having%20second%20thoughts%20about%20what%20was%20considered%20a%20miracle%20economy.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20World%20Economic%20Forum%20in%20Davos%20in%20January%2C%20Trump%20made%20a%20simple%20pitch%20that%20if%20companies%20invested%20in%20American%20manufacturing%20capabilities%2C%20then%20they%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20lowest%20taxation.%20While%20Trump%20has%20not%20made%20good%20on%20his%20campaign%20pledge%E2%80%94a%2060%25%20blanket%20tariff%20on%20Chinese%20merchandise%E2%80%94he%20has%20threatened%20imposition%20of%20a%2010%25%20levy%20from%20February%201%20if%20Beijing%20does%20not%20act%20on%20the%20exports%20of%20ingredients%20for%20fentanyl%2C%20a%20harmful%20synthetic%20opioid.%20Among%20the%20first%20Presidential%20orders%20that%20he%20signed%20was%20a%20comprehensive%20review%20of%20trade%20with%20China%2C%20including%20supply%20chains%20that%20use%20other%20countries%20to%20evade%20exposure%20to%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20100%25%20Rise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20rising%20geopolitical%20tensions%2C%20a%20record%20number%20of%20American%20corporates%E2%80%94as%20many%20as%2030%25%E2%80%94are%20either%20contemplating%20shifting%20out%20some%20operations%20from%20China%20or%20are%20already%20in%20the%20process%20of%20relocating%20elsewhere%2C%20revealed%20the%20annual%20survey%20by%20the%20American%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20in%20China.%20This%20exodus%20of%20America%20Inc%20from%20China%20is%20twice%20as%20big%20as%20in%202020%2C%20when%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20had%20led%20China%20to%20impose%20strict%20lockdowns%20as%20a%20response%20to%20the%20contingency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20factors%20for%20this%20mass%20departure%20is%20that%20the%20bottom%20line%20for%20any%20commercial%20venture%20is%20the%20profits%20it%20makes.%20More%20than%2050%25%20of%20the%20firms%20interviewed%20stated%20that%20they%20were%20barely%20managing%20to%20break%20even%20or%20bore%20huge%20losses%20in%202024.%20This%20has%20affected%20the%20%E2%80%98consumer'%20and%20%E2%80%98services'%20sectors%2C%20where%20the%20figures%20for%20companies%20that%20are%20in%20the%20red%20or%20just%20breaking%20even%20are%2060%25%20and%2057%25%2C%20respectively.%20The%20corresponding%20numbers%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98industrial'%20and%20%E2%80%98technology%20and%20research'%20segments%20are%2048%25%20and%2045%25.%20As%20many%20as%2017%25%20of%20respondents%20revealed%20that%20they%20had%20actively%20begun%20to%20shift%20out%20production%20and%20procurement%20outside%20of%20China%E2%80%94an%20increase%20of%20nearly%2010%20percentage%20points%20since%202020.%20Forty-four%20per%20cent%20cited%20Sino-American%20trade%20rows%20as%20a%20prime%20cause%20for%20this%20development.%20And%2C%20as%20many%20as%2038%25%20of%20the%20respondents%20saw%20developing%20nations%20in%20Asia%2C%20such%20as%20India%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20Thailand%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Indonesia%2C%20as%20preferred%20destinations%20for%20the%20relocation%3B%2018%25%20are%20keen%20to%20reshore%20to%20the%20U.S.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign-owned%20firms%20are%20also%20increasingly%20feeling%20the%20heat%20as%20China%20queers%20the%20playing%20field.%20Nearly%2050%25%20of%20the%20companies%20interviewed%20in%20the%20technology%20sector%20grudge%20that%20local%20Chinese%20ventures%20are%20being%20given%20preference%20over%20them%20in%20the%20research%20and%20development%20and%20advanced%20technology%20sectors.%20In%20the%20same%20segment%2C%20as%20many%20as%2093%25%20of%20businesses%20stated%20that%20lack%20of%20market%20access%20had%20affected%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina%20No%20Longer%20A%20Top%20Investment%20Priority%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20American%20companies%20that%20did%20not%20see%20China%20as%20a%20top%20priority%20in%20their%20investment%20plans%20has%20increased%2C%20reaching%2021%25%20in%202024.%20This%20is%20despite%20China%20pulling%20out%20all%20stops%20to%20improve%20the%20investment%20climate%20in%20recent%20times.%20It%20expanded%20market%20access%20and%20eased%20visas%20and%20investment%20restrictions%20last%20year%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20improve%20investor%20sentiment.%20However%2C%20a%20crackdown%20on%20business%20consultancies%20and%20audit%20firms%20has%20increased%20apprehensions%20among%20foreign%20businesspeople.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20is%20facing%20headwinds%20in%20other%20places%20too.%20As%20Germany%20heads%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20February%2C%20Friedrich%20Merz%2C%20who%20is%20considered%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20the%20country's%20chancellorship%2C%20has%20cautioned%20its%20companies%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Crisk%E2%80%9D%20of%20investing%20in%20China%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20part%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Caxis%20of%20autocracies%E2%80%9D%20that%20did%20not%20adhere%20to%20%E2%80%9Crule%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscontent%20In%20Europe%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20similar%20development%20last%20year%2C%20the%20European%20Union%20(EU)%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20in%20China%20in%20a%20paper%20revealed%20that%20there%20was%20a%20notion%20that%20foreign%20businesses%20operating%20in%20China%20were%20in%20for%20diminishing%20returns%20on%20their%20capital%20invested%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20did%20not%20justify%20the%20increasing%20risks%20of%20operating%20in%20the%20market.%20Investors%20had%20taken%20a%20view%20that%20challenges%20in%20the%20Chinese%20market%20appeared%20to%20be%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpermanent%20nature%E2%80%9D%20that%20forced%20a%20%E2%80%9Csubstantial%20strategic%20rethink%E2%80%9D%20of%20their%20investment.%20Furthermore%2C%20as%20many%20as%2044%25%20of%20EU%20Chamber%20members%20perceived%20bleak%20prospects%20with%20respect%20to%20future%20profitability.%20The%20plummeting%20sentiment%20of%20EU%20members%20was%20ascribed%20to%20regulatory%20issues%2C%20preferences%20in%20government%20procurement%2C%20market%20access%20and%20overcapacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20this%20disillusionment%20with%20China%2C%20there%20could%20be%20an%20opportunity%20for%20India.%20Recently%2C%20tech%20giant%20IBM%20announced%20the%20winding%20up%20of%20its%20research%20operations%20in%20a%20series%20of%20retreats%20from%20China%20after%20nearly%2025%20years%20of%20operations.%20There%20are%20reports%20that%20the%20technology%20major%20plans%20to%20expand%20its%20Indian%20operations.%20Amid%20the%20exodus%20from%20China%2C%20India%20must%20position%20itself%20as%20a%20catchment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EThe%20writer%20is%20a%20China%20Fellow%20at%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation's%20Strategic%20Studies%20Programme)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738131900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fo85uf8s8_china_625x300_29_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fa-record-number-of-us-firms-are-leaving-china-7584723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2