20to%20India%20blew%20up%20off%20the%20Irish%20coast%2C%20killing%20all%20329%20people%20on%20board.%20The%20jet%20disintegrated%20in%20midair%20just%2045%20minutes%20from%20its%20destination%2C%20No%20warning%20or%20emergency%20calls%20were%20issued.%20The%20aircraft%20operating%20the%20flight%20was%20a%20Boeing%20747-237B%20registered%20VT-EFO%20and%20named%20Emperor%20Kanishka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20was%20considered%20the%20deadliest%20aviation%20terrorism%20incident%20until%20the%20September%2011%2C%202001%20attacks%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Most%20of%20the%20passengers%20on%20the%20flight%20were%20Canadian%20citizens%2C%20who%20were%20visiting%20relatives%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20another%20explosion%20was%20reported%20at%20the%20Narita%20airport%20in%20Japan%20claiming%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20baggage%20handlers%2C%20who%20were%20loading%20luggage%20onto%20an%20Air%20India%20aircraft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20suitcase%20bombs%20were%20later%20traced%20back%20to%20Vancouver%2C%20home%20to%20a%20large%20Sikh%20immigrant%20population.%20As%20per%20the%20Canadian%20government%20reports%2C%20the%20bombings%20were%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20carried%20out%20by%20Canadian-based%20Sikh%20separatists%20in%20revenge%20for%20the%20Indian%20Army's%20'Operation%20Blue%20Star'%20at%20Golden%20Temple%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20months%20after%20the%20disaster%2C%20two%20suspects--%20Talwinder%20Singh%20Parmar%20and%20%C2%A0Inderjit%20Singh%20Reyat%20were%20arrested.%20Charges%20against%20Parmar%2C%20who%20was%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20masterminded%20the%20attack%2C%20were%20dropped%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20accused--Ripudaman%20Singh%20Malik%20and%20Ajaib%20Singh%20Bagri%2C%20were%20arrested%20in%202000%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20acquitted%20on%20insufficient%20evidence%20in%202005.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInderjit%20Singh%20Reyat%20is%20the%20only%20person%20to%20have%20been%20convicted%20in%20the%20plot%2C%20for%20making%20the%20bombs%20and%20for%20lying%20at%20the%20trials%20of%20Malik%20and%20Bagri.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738131060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Ffel7na5g_ripudaman-singh_625x300_16_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhitman-sentenced-to-life-for-murder-of-air-india-kanishka-bombing-suspect-ripudaman-singh-malik-7584770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20contract%20killer%20in%20Canada%20was%20convicted%20on%20Tuesday%20(local%20time)%20of%20murdering%20an%20acquitted%20suspect%20in%201985%20Air%20India%20bombings%20that%20had%20claimed%20331%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arithmetic%20Skills%20Have%20Shown%2030%25%20Improvement%20In%20Schools%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2F82-of-children-aged-14-to-16-know-to-use-smartphones-aser-2024-report-7578874%5C%22%3EAnnual%20Status%20of%20Education%20Report%20(ASER)%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024%20was%20released%20on%20Tuesday%20highlighting%20significant%20improvement%20in%20reading%20and%20arithmetic%20skills%20of%20students.%20According%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20Survey%2C%20the%20Grade%203%20students%20have%20recorded%20advancement%20in%20both%20reading%20and%20arithmetic%20skills%20in%20government%20schools.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CIn%202024%2C%20the%20percentage%20of%20Grade%203%20students%20able%20to%20read%20Grade%202-level%20text%20rose%20by%20an%20impressive%2043%20per%20cent%2C%20from%2016.3%20per%20cent%20in%202022%20to%2023.4%20per%20cent.%20This%20recovery%20follows%20a%20prolonged%20decline%20due%20to%20learning%20loss%20during%20Covid%2C%20with%20basic%20reading%20levels%20at%2020.9%20per%20cent%20in%202018%20before%20slipping%20further%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20official%20statement.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%E2%80%9CArithmetic%20skills%20have%20shown%20a%2030%20per%20cent%20improvement%3A%20the%20proportion%20of%20Grade%203%20children%20capable%20of%20performing%20basic%20subtraction%20rose%20from%2025.9%20per%20cent%20in%202021%20to%2033.7%20per%20cent%20in%202024%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20further%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20government's%20ambitious%20NIPUN%20Bharat%20Mission%20(National%20Initiative%20for%20Proficiency%20in%20Reading%20with%20Understanding%20and%20Numeracy)%2C%20launched%20in%202021%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20the%20reason%20behind%20this%20transitional%20shift.%20The%20objective%20of%20this%20mission%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20children%20are%20able%20to%20achieve%20grade-level%20reading%20and%20numeracy%20skills%20by%20the%20end%20of%20Grade%202.%20The%20focus%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20policy's%20guidelines%2C%20which%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20highest%20priority%20must%20be%20to%20achieve%20universal%20foundational%20literacy%20and%20numeracy%20(FLN)%20in%20primary%20school%20and%20beyond%20by%202026-27.%20%E2%80%9D%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20order%20to%20achieve%20the%20results%2C%20the%20government%20had%20diverted%20Rs%209%2C235%20crores%20under%20the%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20framework%20between%202021%20and%202025.%20Of%20these%2C%20over%20Rs%202%2C000%20crores%20were%20allocated%20annually%20for%20teacher%20training%2C%20assessments%2C%20and%20high-quality%20learning%20materials.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20government%20school%20enrollment%20seen%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20years%20seems%20to%20have%20reversed.%20Private%20school%20enrollment%20has%20been%20steadily%20rising%20since%202006%20in%20rural%20India.%20The%20proportion%20of%206-14-year-olds%20enrolled%20in%20private%20schools%20rose%20from%2018.7%20per%20cent%20in%202006%20to%2030.8%20per%20cent%20in%202014%20and%20stayed%20at%20that%20level%20in%202018.%20During%20the%20pandemic%20years%2C%20there%20was%20a%20big%20jump%20in%20government%20school%20enrollment%20with%20the%20proportion%20of%206-14-year-old%20children%20enrolled%20in%20government%20schools%20rising%20from%2065.6%20per%20cent%20in%202018%20to%2072.9%20per%20cent%20in%202022.%20This%20number%20is%20back%20to%2066.8%20per%20cent%20in%202024.%20This%20almost%20complete%20reversal%20back%20to%202018%20levels%20is%20seen%20across%20grades%20as%20well%20as%20gender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20summarise%2C%20ASER%202024%20brings%20good%20news%20on%20the%20enrollment%20front.%20Out%20of%20school%20numbers%20for%20older%20age%20groups%20that%20had%20been%20falling%20steadily%20are%20well%20below%20their%202018%20levels%20though%20marginally%20higher%20than%20the%202022%20estimates%2C%20and%20government%20and%20private%20school%20enrollment%20is%20back%20to%202018%20levels.%20This%20seems%20to%20confirm%20that%20the%20increase%20in%20government%20school%20enrollment%20observed%20during%20the%20Covid%20years%20was%20driven%20more%20by%20necessity%20rather%20than%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Annual%20Status%20of%20Education%20Report%20(ASER)%202024%20is%20a%20nationwide%20rural%20household%20survey%20that%20reached%206%2C49%2C491%20children%20in%2017%2C997%20villages%20across%20605%20rural%20districts%20in%20India.%20Facilitated%20by%20an%20NGO%2C%20%26quot%3BPratham%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20each%20surveyed%20district%2C%20a%20local%20organisation%20or%20institution%20conducted%20the%20survey.%3Cbr%3E%5CnFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20nationwide%20household%20survey%20had%20a%20section%20on%20digital%20literacy%2C%20which%20applied%20to%20older%20children%20in%20the%2014-16%20age%20group.%20It%20included%20self-reported%20questions%20on%20access%2C%20ownership%20and%20use%20of%20smartphones%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20one-on-one%20assessment%20of%20some%20basic%20digital%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20agencies)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738130820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-02%2Ferinh244_delhi-school-generic_625x300_19_February_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Faser-report-2024-records-improvement-in-reading-and-arithmetic-skills-7584657%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20had%20diverted%20Rs%209%2C235%20crores%20under%20the%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20framework%20between%202021%20and%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pregnant%20Maharashtra%20Woman%20Detected%20With%20Rare%20'Fetus%20In%20Fetu'%20Condition%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2032-year-old%20pregnant%20woman%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Buldhana%20district%20has%20been%20detected%20with%20'fetus%20in%20fetu'%2C%20an%20extremely%20rare%20condition%20in%20which%20a%20malformed%20fetus%20is%20located%20within%20the%20body%20of%20another%20fetus%2C%20an%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rare%20congenital%20anomaly%20was%20detected%20a%20few%20days%20back%20when%20the%20woman%2C%20who%20is%2035%20weeks%20pregnant%2C%20went%20to%20Buldhana%20District%20Women's%20Hospital%20for%20a%20regular%20check-up%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20condition%20during%20the%20woman's%20sonography%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObstetrician%20and%20gynaecologist%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20Dr%20Prasad%20Agarwal%2C%20told%20reporters%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20'fetus%20in%20fetu'%20is%20one%20of%20the%20rarest%20cases%20--%20one%20in%20five%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20about%20200%20such%20cases%20have%20been%20reported%20(across%20the%20world)%20till%20now%2C%20that%20too%20after%20delivery%2C%20including%2010-15%20cases%20in%20India%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20was%20lucky%20and%20vigilant%20enough%20to%20notice%20something%20very%20unusual%20with%20this%20baby%2C%20which%20is%20almost%20of%2035%20weeks%2C%20grossly%20normal%20growing%20fetus%20with%20a%20few%20bones%20and%20fetus-like%20structure%20in%20its%20abdomen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20struck%20me%20immediately%20that%20this%20is%20not%20normal.%20It%20was%20'fetus%20in%20fetu'%2C%20one%20of%20the%20rarest%20cases%20in%20the%20world.%20We%20had%20asked%20for%20a%20second%20opinion%20and%20the%20case%20was%20confirmed%20by%20radiologist%20Dr%20Shruti%20Thorat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20a%20medical%20facility%20in%20neighbouring%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhajinagar%20for%20a%20safe%20delivery%20and%20further%20procedure%2C%20the%20hospital%20authorities%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738130520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fjtnm85h_pregnant-woman_625x300_01_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpregnant-maharashtra-woman-detected-with-rare-fetus-in-fetu-condition-7584695%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2032-year-old%20pregnant%20woman%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Buldhana%20district%20has%20been%20detected%20with%20'fetus%20in%20fetu'%2C%20an%20extremely%20rare%20condition%20in%20which%20a%20malformed%20fetus%20is%20located%20within%20the%20body%20of%20another%20fetus%2C%20an%20official%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Roman%20Abramovich%20could%20owe%20UK%20%C2%A31bn%20over%20tax%20dodge%20that%20helped%20bankroll%20Chelsea%20FC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738130408000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Ff909%2Flive%2F98585230-dd72-11ef-bc01-8f2c83dad217.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgrn