20most%20downloaded%20free%20app%20on%20Apple's%20App%20Store.%20The%20AI%20is%20optimised%20for%20tasks%20like%20math%20and%20coding%2C%20making%20it%20a%20strong%20competitor%20in%20the%20AI%20space.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20Western%20models%2C%20DeepSeek%20follows%20China's%20strict%20censorship%20rules.%20When%20asked%20about%20sensitive%20topics%2C%20it%20avoids%20direct%20answers%2C%20reflecting%20government%20control%20over%20digital%20content.%20Despite%20this%2C%20experts%20praise%20its%20efficiency%2C%20as%20it%20uses%20advanced%20and%20lower-grade%20chips%20to%20deliver%20high%20performance%20at%20a%20lower%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeepSeek's%20vision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20founder%2C%20Liang%20Wenfeng%2C%20a%20Zhejiang%20University%20graduate%20with%20a%20background%20in%20electronic%20engineering%20and%20computer%20science%2C%20built%20his%20reputation%20in%20the%20finance%20sector%20before%20venturing%20to%20AI.%20He%20has%20been%20vocal%20about%20China's%20need%20to%20innovate%20rather%20than%20imitate%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20real%20gap%20between%20Chinese%20and%20American%20AI%20lies%20in%20originality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20ambitions%20align%20with%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping's%20push%20to%20make%20AI%20a%20national%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlobal%20reactions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20rise%20has%20not%20gone%20unnoticed%20by%20global%20markets%20and%20policymakers.%20The%20launch%20of%20its%20AI%20assistant%20coincided%20with%20a%20historic%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnvidia-loses-nearly-600-billion-as-chinas-deepseek-jolts-tech-shares-7575388%5C%22%3E%24600%20billion%20market%20value%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Nvidia%2C%20a%20key%20player%20in%20AI%20chip%20production.%20The%20US%20government's%20ongoing%20restrictions%20on%20advanced%20chip%20exports%20to%20China%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20