computer%20science%20but%20eventually%20excelled.%20She%20then%20earned%20a%20spot%20at%20Peking%20University's%20Institute%20of%20Computational%20Linguistics%2C%20publishing%20eight%20papers%20at%20the%20prestigious%20ACL%20conference%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20remarkable%20achievement%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20tech%20giants%20Alibaba%20and%20Xiaomi%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20her%20future%20collaborations.%20As%20a%20researcher%20at%20Alibaba's%20DAMO%20Academy%2C%20Luo%20spearheaded%20the%20development%20of%20the%20multilingual%20pre-training%20model%20VECO%20and%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20the%20open-source%20AliceMind%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20joined%20DeepSeek%20in%202022.%20Her%20expertise%20in%20natural%20language%20processing%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20developing%20DeepSeek-V2%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hailed%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20rival%20ChatGPT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20her%20stint%20at%20DeepSeek%2C%20Luo's%20exceptional%20skills%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20Xiaomi's%20founder%2C%20Lei%20Jun%2C%20who%20offered%20her%20an%20annual%20compensation%20package%20of%2010%20million%20yuan%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Ftech%2Fbig-tech%2Farticle%2F3296626%2Fhow-tech-start-deepseek-emerged-unlikely-game-changer-us-china-ai-war%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20was%20founded%20in%202023%20by%2040-year-old%20Liang%20Wenfeng%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20China.%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BThe%20Chinese%20AI%20chatbot%20is%20making%20waves%20in%20the%20AI%20world%20with%20its%20impressive%20large%20language%20models%20(LLMs)%20developed%20at%20a%20significantly%20lower%20cost%20than%20its%20global%20competitors.%C2%A0DeepSeek-V3's%20performance%20rivals%20that%20of%20other%20top%20LLMs%2C%20including%20Llama%203.1%20and%20Qwen%202.5%2C%20while%20matching%20GPT-4o%20and%20Claude%203.5%20Sonnet.%C2%A0DeepSeek's%20success%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20its%20innovative%20approach%20to%20AI%20development%2C%20including%20its%20use%20of%20open-source%20models%20and%20low-cost%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20DeepSeek%2C%20its%20R1%20model%20has%20demonstrated%20superior%20performance%20compared%20to%20OpenAI's%20o1-mini%20model%20across%20multiple%20benchmarks.%20Further%2C%20research%20conducted%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fartificialanalysis.ai%2F%5C%22%3EArtificial%20Analysis%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0reveals%20that%20DeepSeek's%20R1%20model%20surpasses%20models%20developed%20by%20tech%20giants%20Google%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Anthropic%20in%20terms%20of%20overall%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20launch%20last%20week%2C%20the%20DeepSeek%20app%20has%20surged%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20US%20app%20store%20charts%2C%20surpassing%20ChatGPT%20as%20the%20most%20downloaded%20free%20app.%20The%20meteoric%20rise%20of%20DeepSeek%20has%20sent%20ripples%20through%20the%20US%20tech%20market%2C%20with%20shares%20in%20AI-related%20firms%20such%20as%20Nvidia%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20and%20Meta%20experiencing%20a%20decline%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738126140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F10vnj7vo_luo-fuli_625x300_29_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeet-luo-fuli-the-29-year-old-ai-prodigy-behind-deepseeks-global-success-7584116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Her%20expertise%20in%20natural%20language%20processing%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20developing%20DeepSeek-V2%2C%20which%20has%20been%20hailed%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20rival%20ChatGPT.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fmeet-luo-fuli-the-29-year-old-ai-prodigy-behind-deepseeks-global-s