0across%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20military.%3Cp%3EJim%20WATSON%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPresident%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20to%20rename%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20federal%20government%20and%20military%20are%20already%20embracing%20the%20order%2C%20and%20Google%20Maps%20indicated%20it%20would%20also%20reflect%20the%20change.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20changing%20maps%20and%20charts%20isn't%20a%20simple%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchuck-schumer-renaming-gulf-mexico-trump-lowering-costs-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erename%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20already%20resulting%20in%20changes%20across%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20military.%20Google%20Maps%20has%20indicated%20it%20would%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20federal%20process%20isn't%20as%20simple%20as%20crossing%20out%20the%20old%20name%20and%20writing%20in%20a%20new%20one.%20It's%20a%20complicated%20switch%20across%20the%20bureaucracy%2C%20involving%20a%20top-down%20effort%20to%20update%20official%20documents%2C%20communications%2C%20maps%2C%20and%20charts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20first%20day%20back%20in%20office%20as%20president%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Frestoring-names-that-honor-american-greatness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20issued%20an%20executive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20%26quot%3Brestoring%20names%20that%20honor%20American%20greatness%2C%26quot%3B%20directing%20the%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Interior%20to%20implement%20a%20change%20to%20the%20area%20of%20the%20US%20continental%20shelf%20%26quot%3Bextending%20to%20Mexico%20and%20Cuba%26quot%3B%20and%20remove%20all%20mentions%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20across%20%26quot%3Ball%20federal%20references.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executive%20order%20also%20included%20the%20reversal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fobama-mckinley-denali-name-boehner-portman-kasich-2015-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eformer%20President%20Barack%20Obama's%20naming%20of%20Denali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20North%20America's%20highest%20mountain%20peak%20located%20in%20Alaska%2C%20to%20Mount%20McKinley%20in%20honor%20of%20former%20President%20William%20McKinley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20has%20long%20been%20debated%20and%20satirized.%20However%2C%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20US%20has%20directly%20acted%20to%20change%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223697%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20Coast%20Guard%20Cutter%20Pablo%20Valent%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20blue%20waters%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20waiting%20against%20a%20cloudy%20blue%20sky.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679918f1eb4be2fff9a27785%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222708%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Coast%20Guard%20Cutter%20Pablo%20Valent%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20blue%20waters%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20which%20is%20being%20renamed%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America.%3Cp%3EUS%20Coast%20Guard%20photo%20by%20Petty%20Officer%201st%20Class%20Logan%20Kellogg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20Republicans%2C%20including%20Florida%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis%20and%20Georgia%20Rep.%20Marjorie%20Taylor%20Green%20have%20embraced%20and%20lauded%20the%20move%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit's%20also%20been%20met%20with%20backlash%20and%20confusion%20from%20some%20internationally.%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20said%20last%20week%20that%20%26quot%3Bfor%20us%20and%20for%20the%20whole%20world%2C%20it%20is%20still%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico.%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2F2025%2F01%2F23%2Fbritain-will-not-recognise-trump-new-name-gulf-of-mexico%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReporting%20from%20The%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%20indicated%20that%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20won't%20recognize%20the%20name%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Mexico's%20Sheinbaum%20joked%20that%20because%20a%20world%20map%20from%201607%20%E2%80%94%20169%20years%20before%20the%20US%20was%20founded%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparts-us-america-mexicana-mexican-president-says-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elabeled%20North%20America%20as%20Mexican%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20perhaps%20the%20continent%20should%20be%20named%20as%20such.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20military%2C%20the%20change%20to%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20quickly%20implemented.%20Sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20internal%20documentation%20and%20public-facing%20communications%20are%20already%20updated%20or%20in%20the%20process%20of%20being%20updated%2C%20with%20map%20and%20chart%20changes%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doi.gov%2Fpressreleases%2Finterior-department-advances-restoration-historic-names-honoring-american-greatness%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20the%20Interior%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20efforts%20were%20underway%20to%20make%20the%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20Interior%20Department%2C%20the%20Board%20on%20Geographic%20Names%20has%20purview%20over%20names%20for%20federal%20use%2C%20but%20that's%20only%20binding%20to%20federal%20departments%20and%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20the%20board%20and%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20would%20act%20immediately%20to%20update%20the%20Geographical%20Names%20Information%20System%2C%20a%20database%20of%20more%20than%20two%20million%20physical%20and%20cultural%20features%20throughout%20the%20US%20and%20its%20territories.%20The%20Department%20of%20State%20would%20update%20the%20Geographic%20Names%20Server%2C%20which%20defines%20geographic%C2%A0feature%20names%20outside%20of%20the%20US.%20But%20it's%20up%20to%20each%20agency%20and%20office%20to%20update%20their%20websites%20and%20information%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20US%20Navy%20spokesperson%20said%20once%20the%20internal%20systems%20the%20Navy%20gets%20its%20information%20from%20are%20updated%2C%20its%20maps%20and%20charts%20will%20be%20updated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224379%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20an%20old%20map%20showing%20the%20American%20content%20with%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BMexican%20America.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67991a89eb4be2fff9a27ad7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222791%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20joked%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20North%20America%20should%20be%20renamed%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Trump%20proposing%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%20name.%3Cp%3EALFREDO%20ESTRELLA%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FNewsFromGoogle%2Fstatus%2F1884012692048166951%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%20that%20Google%20Maps%20would%20reflect%20the%20ordered%20name%20changes%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%20and%20Mount%20McKinley%20once%20the%20Geographic%20Names%20Information%20System%20is%20updated%2C%20in%20accordance%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20longstanding%20practice%20of%20applying%20name%20changes%20when%20they%20have%20been%20updated%20in%20official%20government%20sources.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-maps-ai-features-reviews-waze-update-gemini-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20Maps%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%20see%20the%20official%20local%20name%20in%20their%20region%20when%20nomenclature%20varies%20between%20countries%2C%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%20sees%20both%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changing%20of%20some%20other%20maps%20and%20charts%20may%20involve%20a%20longer%20process.%20The%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20engaging%20with%20the%20Board%20on%20Geographic%20Names%20for%20further%20guidance%20on%20the%20implementation%2C%20Scott%20Smullen%2C%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20NOAA%20Communications%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20from%20there%2C%20specifically%20how%20quickly%20maps%20will%20be%20updated%20across%20the%20federal%20government%20and%20military%2C%20appears%20fairly%20complex%2C%20requiring%20updating%20every%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20oil%20rig%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20with%20a%20sunset%20in%20the%20background%2C%20casting%20a%20red%20glow%20on%20the%20sky%20and%20water.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6799188beb4be2fff9a2766b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221178%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20gulf%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20vital%20assets%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US'%20history%20and%20economy%2C%20the%20Interior%20Department%20said%2C%20with%20rich%20fisheries%2C%20vast%20oil%20and%20natural%20gas%20reserves%2C%20and%20trade%20routes.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Trump's%20executive%20order%2C%20the%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Interior%20has%2030%20days%20to%20implement%20the%20name%20change%20and%20ensure%20%26quot%3Ball%20federal%20references%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%2C%20including%20on%20agency%20maps%2C%20contracts%2C%20and%20other%20documents%20and%20communications%20shall%20reflect%20its%20renaming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Coast%20Guard's%20District%208%2C%20which%20oversees%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20area%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bacting%20in%20compliance%26quot%3B%20with%20Trump's%20executive%20order.%20Just%20a%20day%20after%20Trump's%20executive%20order%2C%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20began%20using%20the%20term%20when%20announcing%20deployed%20assets%20to%20the%20maritime%20border%20between%20Texas%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20time%2C%20Apple%20Maps%20hasn't%20renamed%20the%20body%20of%20water.%20The%20Associated%20Press%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ap.org%2Fthe-definitive-source%2Fannouncements%2Fap-style-guidance-on-gulf-of-mexico-mount-mckinley%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20that%20it%20would%20still%20use%20the%20name%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20while%20also%20acknowledging%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%20in%20its%20style%20guide.%20It%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20a%20global%20news%20agency%20that%20disseminates%20news%20around%20the%20world%2C%20the%20AP%20must%20ensure%20that%20place%20names%20and%20geography%20are%20easily%20recognizable%20to%20all%20audiences.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI's%20style%20is%20consistent%2C%20using%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Trump's%20executive%20order%20is%20only%20effective%20domestically%2C%20other%20nations%20and%20international%20organizations%20could%20continue%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20region%20as%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20and%20similar%20variations%20exist%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20Persian%20Gulf%20located%20south%20of%20Iran%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20long%20been%20the%20site%20of%20controversy%2C%20with%20some%20nearby%20Arab%20countries%20like%20Saudi%20Arabia%20calling%20it%20the%20Arabian%20Gulf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanging-us-maps-to-gulf-of-america-isnt-simple-process-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738097884000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67990bdaeb4be2fff9a2689b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanging-us-maps-to-gulf-of-america-isnt-simple-process-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20federal%20government%2C%20including%20the%20military%2C%20is%20changing%20the%20name%20on%20maps%20to%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America.%26quot%3B%20Even%20Google%20suggested%20it%20would%20make%20the%20change.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Chris%20Panella%2CSarah%20Jackson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A730%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanging-us-maps-to-gulf-of-america-isnt-simple-process-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20complete%20timeline%20of%20Drake's%20rise%20to%20stardom%2C%20from%20starring%20on%20'Degrassi'%20to%20his%20record-breaking%20reign%20as%20a%20rapper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222629%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22drake%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5bce00e4c762190ba935cbf6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221971%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDrake%20is%20the%20stage%20name%20of%20Aubrey%20Drake%20Graham.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Winter%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Coachella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDrake%20has%20one%20of%20the%20most%20unexpected%20and%20impressive%20careers%20in%20the%20music%20industry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20now-iconic%20rapper%20released%20his%20first%20mixtape%20in%202006%20and%20left%20%26quot%3BDegrassi%